# Cursor Rules — Next.js Fullstack Project

## Tech Stack

- **Framework**: Next.js 14+ (App Router)
- **Language**: TypeScript (strict mode)
- **Styling**: Tailwind CSS + ShadCN UI
- **ORM**: Prisma
- **Database**: MongoDB Atlas
- **Data Fetching**: Axios + TanStack Query (React Query)

